As per our phone communication, we're looking to offer quantitative
research projects to IIT Madras students with the following incentives 

 INR 65,000 monthly compensation plus performancebased bonus.
 Flexibly work from any Internetaccessible location at any time of the
day.
 Invaluable learning and networking opportunities with global hedge fund
managers.
 Access to a robust, proprietary technology platform that enables users to
efficiently explore and convert their creative ideas into Alpha signals
that may be traded in the real world.
 Mentoring and guidance from experienced quantitative researchers.
 Fulltime offers for top performers.

We'd like to communicate this opportunity to all IIT Madras students via
departmentspecific group mailing lists / student groups etc. And, we'd
appreciate any assistance in ensuring that it reaches all the students.

